				<outline text="Paul Boutin will moderate the syndication panel at SuperNova on Thursday with &lt;a href=&quot;http://blogs.salon.com/0000014/2004/06/21.html#a628&quot;&gt;Scott Rosenberg&lt;/a&gt;, David Sifry, and Tim Bray, who is one of two chairs of the Atom working group." created="Tue, 22 Jun 2004 05:14:49 GMT" type="outline"/>
