				<outline text="The Skelecosm: &lt;a href=&quot;http://skelecosm.typepad.com/blog/2004/06/why_i_chose_rss.html&quot;&gt;Why I Chose RSS 2.0&lt;/a&gt;. &quot;Which standard is easy enough to implement in Notepad, and guaranteed to work everywhere?&quot;" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2004 22:26:33 GMT" type="outline"/>
