				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.kron4.com/Global/story.asp?S=1919936&amp;nav=5D7lNgIR&quot;&gt;Bay City News&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;San Francisco downtown streets are expected to become the scene of anti-war demonstrations on Saturday.&quot;" created="Sat, 05 Jun 2004 17:33:34 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.theregister.co.uk/2004/06/04/biometric_drm/&quot;&gt;Orlowski&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;Not content with asking for an arm and a leg from consumers and artists, the music industry now wants your fingerprints, too.&quot;" created="Sat, 05 Jun 2004 21:43:06 GMT" type="outline"/>
				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nytimes.com/2004/06/06/politics/campaign/06VEEP.html?ex=1401854400&amp;en=af9b8aa763b3c02b&amp;ei=5007&amp;partner=USERLAND&quot;&gt;NY Times&lt;/a&gt;: &quot;Kerry is able to unleash a kennel full of attack dogs, all standing to gain from impressing the man who could be their boss.&quot;" created="Sat, 05 Jun 2004 20:29:28 GMT" type="outline"/>
